tras/7fb2b130c3c54ef0d98909684243b3e4.webm?t=1766164461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054720/extras/7fb2b130c3c54ef0d98909684243b3e4.mp4?t=1766164461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Roast fish in the pavilion:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054720/extras/57adacb13cf7e200cdd7719114dc5449.poster.avif?t=1766164461\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054720/extras/57adacb13cf7e200cdd7719114dc5449.webm?t=1766164461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054720/extras/57adacb13cf7e200cdd7719114dc5449.mp4?t=1766164461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Swimming：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054720/extras/c8353f3cd0c3125ee20985c28d57dd4f.poster.avif?t=1766164461\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054720/extras/c8353f3cd0c3125ee20985c28d57dd4f.webm?t=1766164461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054720/extras/c8353f3cd0c3125ee20985c28d57dd4f.mp4?t=1766164461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
